Package de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.melt.matching_base.typetransformer

Class AlignmentAndParameters

java.lang.Object
de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.melt.matching_base.typetransformer.AlignmentAndParameters
public class AlignmentAndParameters
extends Object
Due to the fact that a matcher can only return one value, but alignment and parameters can be changed, an extra object is necessary. If you don't care about the updated parameters you can just return the alignment.
